wer distribution companies, as well as operates mines for bauxite ores located in Gujarat. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as Orient Abrasives Limited and changed its name to Orient Ceratech Limited in May 2023. Orient Ceratech Limited was incorporated in 1971 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}